reviewText: This video, coupled with our local aquarium, have given my preschool daughter an incredible love for the oceans. She already wants to be a marine biologist and her best "imaginary" friend is her fellow diver, "Annie." An all-around fun and educational film about ocean creatures and the diversity of life in the oceans. Love it!!
I thought it would be about diversity. It touches the topic, but it is really about under sea life.
